# Test your FastAPI endpoints

GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/
Accept: application/json

###

GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/hello/User
Accept: application/json

###

### Test the main chat endpoint
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Hola",
  "user_id": "test_user_1",
  "channel": "postman_test"
}

### Test english courses question
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "quiero saber de los cursos de ingles",
  "user_id": "test_user_1",
  "channel": "postman_test"
}

### Test contextual follow up question
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "si, los precios",
  "user_id": "test_user_1",
  "channel": "postman_test"
}

### Read standard metrics
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/metrics
